---
title: Crispy Chicken Parmesan Salad with Spinach and Roasted Potatoes
description: Best part of chicken Parmesan? The thick layer of gooey, creamy cheese melted on top of crispy chicken. In this dish, we’ve recreated the same dreamy combination but given it a lighter twist by tossing in some greens. Needless to say, it’s the best of both worlds.
